{
  "chapter": 6,
  "chapter_summary": "二月初一凌晨，李庄慈恩寺雪后钟梵清冷。司马超群饮冷酒，卓东来以酒水相溶暗示自己已让高渐飞因女子而软弱，并维护司马超群不败。大雁塔下，高渐飞心空如麻仍欲拔泪痕剑挑战，司马超群看出他已败而不愿杀他。神秘灰衣人从塔上救走高渐飞，卓东来说出萧泪血之名。塔顶，萧泪血揭示泪痕剑出鞘必饮血、凶兆来自铸剑大师泪痕，并告诫公平决斗早被势力破坏，若要胜司马只能刺杀。高渐飞追问剑与箱子的秘密无果，萧泪血离去后，他思念蝶舞，终于想起朱猛在洛阳。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "卓东来",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "text": "现在就开始喝酒是不是嫌太早了一点？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "卓东来",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "text": "今天你就算要喝酒，是不是也应该等到晚一点的时候再喝？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "司马超群",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "卓东来",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "text": "因为你马上就要遇到一个很强的对手，很可能比我们想像中还要强得多。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "司马超群",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "卓东来",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "text": "所以就算一定要喝酒，最少也应该等到和他交过手之后再喝。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "司马超群",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "text": "我为什么要等到那时候，你难道忘了我是永远不败的司马超群？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "司马超群",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "text": "我反正不会败的，就算喝得烂醉如泥，也绝不会败，因为你一定早就安排好了，把什么事都安排好了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "司马超群",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "text": "那个叫高渐飞的小子，反正已非败不可，非死不可。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "司马超群",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "text": "这一次你能不能告诉我，你究竟是怎么安排的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "卓东来",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "text": "有些事本来就随时会发生的，用不着我安排也一样。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "司马超群",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "text": "你只不过让高渐飞很偶然的遇到了一两件这样的事而已。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "卓东来",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "text": "每个人都难免会偶然遇到一些这样的事。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "卓东来",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "text": "不管谁遇到，都同样无可奈何。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "卓东来",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "text": "这是不是很自然的事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "司马超群",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "卓东来",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "text": "有些人一样。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "卓东来",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "text": "有些人相遇之后，也会像酒和水般相溶。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "司马超群",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "text": "可是酒水相溶之后，酒就会变得淡了，水也会变了质。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "卓东来",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "text": "人也一样。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "卓东来",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "text": "完全一样。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "司马超群",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "卓东来",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "text": "有些人相遇之后也会变的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "卓东来",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "text": "有些人遇到某一个人之后，就会变得软弱一点。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "司马超群",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "text": "就像是掺了水的酒？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "卓东来",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "司马超群",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "text": "所以你就让高渐飞偶然遇到了这么样一个像水一样的人？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "卓东来",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "卓东来",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "text": "偶然间相遇，偶然间别离，谁也无可奈何。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "卓东来",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "text": "天地间本来就有很多事都是这样子的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "司马超群",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "text": "你为什么要对我这么好？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "司马超群",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "text": "为什么要把我的每件事都安排得这么好？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "卓东来",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "text": "因为你是司马超群。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "卓东来",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "text": "因为司马超群是永远不能败的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "司马超群",
      "listener": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "text": "你就是高渐飞？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "speaker_name": "高渐飞",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "text": "我就是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "speaker_name": "高渐飞",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "text": "你为什么走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "司马超群",
      "listener": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "text": "因为我不想杀你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "司马超群",
      "listener": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "text": "在我的剑下，败就是死。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "司马超群",
      "listener": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "text": "其实现在你自己也应该知道你已经败了，因为你这个人已经是个空的人，就好像一口装米的麻袋，已经被人把袋子里的米倒空了一样。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "卓东来",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "text": "你既然本来就不想杀他，又何必再去追？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "司马超群",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "text": "那个人是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "卓东来",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "text": "哪个人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "司马超群",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "text": "你应该知道我说的是谁，你不让我去追，就因为你怕他。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "卓东来",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "text": "武林中高手辈出，各有绝技，高手对决时，胜负之分通常都是靠他们当时的情况和机遇。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "卓东来",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "text": "自从小李飞刀退隐后，真正能够无敌于天下的高手，几乎已经没有了。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "司马超群",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "text": "是几乎没有？还是绝对没有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "卓东来",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "text": "我也不能确定。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "卓东来",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "text": "只不过有人告诉过我，在这个世界上，某一个不知名的地方，有一个这么样的人。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "司马超群",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "司马超群",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "text": "你说的这个人是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "卓东来",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "text": "他姓萧，易水萧萧的萧，",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "卓东来",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "text": "他的名字叫萧泪血。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "歌声",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "森森剑气，萧萧易水；\n\n英雄无泪，化作碧血。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "歌声",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "浪子三唱，只唱英雄；\n\n浪子无根，英雄无泪。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "司马超群",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "text": "萧泪血！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "司马超群",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "text": "他是个什么样的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "司马超群",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "text": "你有没有看到过他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "卓东来",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "text": "我没有。谁也没有看见过他。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "卓东来",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_chao_qun",
      "text": "就算看见过他的人，也不会知道他是谁。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "speaker_name": "高渐飞",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "text": "是你，又是你，",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "speaker_name": "高渐飞",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "text": "你究竟是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "speaker_name": "高渐飞",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "text": "为什么忽然又把我弄到这么样一个见鬼的地方来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "speaker_name": "萧泪血",
      "listener": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "text": "这个地方见不到鬼的，可是不把你弄到这地方来，我就要见到一个鬼了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "speaker_name": "萧泪血",
      "listener": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "text": "一个新死的鬼。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "speaker_name": "高渐飞",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "text": "这个新死的鬼就是我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "speaker_name": "萧泪血",
      "listener": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "text": "大概是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "speaker_name": "高渐飞",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "text": "你怎么知道我一定会死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "speaker_name": "萧泪血",
      "listener": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "text": "因为你的剑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "speaker_name": "萧泪血",
      "listener": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "text": "往事如烟，昔日的名剑已沉埋，你的这柄剑已经是当今天下无双的利器，近五百年来没有任何一柄剑可以比得上它。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "speaker_name": "高渐飞",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "speaker_name": "萧泪血",
      "listener": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "text": "铸造它的人，是欧冶子之后第一位大师，也是当时的第一位剑客。\n\n可是终他的一生，从来也没有用过这柄剑，甚至没有拔出鞘来给人看过。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "speaker_name": "高渐飞",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "speaker_name": "萧泪血",
      "listener": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "text": "因为这柄剑太凶，只要一出鞘，必饮人血。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "speaker_name": "萧泪血",
      "listener": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "text": "此剑出炉时，那位大师就已看出剑上的凶兆，一种无法可解的凶兆，所以他忍不住流下泪来，滴落在这柄剑上，化做了泪痕。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "speaker_name": "高渐飞",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "text": "剑锋上的泪痕就是这样来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "speaker_name": "萧泪血",
      "listener": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "speaker_name": "高渐飞",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "text": "那位大师既然已看出它的凶煞，为什么不索性毁了它？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "speaker_name": "萧泪血",
      "listener": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "text": "因为这柄剑铸造得实在太完美，",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "speaker_name": "萧泪血",
      "listener": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "text": "有谁能忍心下得了手，把自己一生心血化成的精萃毁于一旦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "speaker_name": "萧泪血",
      "listener": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "text": "何况剑已出炉，已成神器，就算能毁了它的形，也毁不了它的神了，迟早总有一天，它的预兆，还是会灵验。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "speaker_name": "高渐飞",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "text": "天地间本来就有些事物是永远无法消灭的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "speaker_name": "萧泪血",
      "listener": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "text": "所以今天你只要拔出这柄剑，就必将死在这柄剑下。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "speaker_name": "萧泪血",
      "listener": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "text": "因为你今天绝对不是司马超群的对手。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "speaker_name": "萧泪血",
      "listener": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "text": "现在你总该已经明白，就算是公平的决斗，也不是完全公平的。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "speaker_name": "高渐飞",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "speaker_name": "萧泪血",
      "listener": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "text": "一个人到达了某种地步，有了某种势力后，就能够制造出一些事情来，削弱对手的力量，使自己获胜。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "speaker_name": "萧泪血",
      "listener": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "text": "这种事通常都是非常令人痛苦的。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "speaker_name": "萧泪血",
      "listener": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "text": "所以如果你真的想对付司马超群，唯一的方法就是出其不意，将他刺杀于剑下。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "speaker_name": "萧泪血",
      "listener": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "text": "因为你根本没有跟他公平决斗的机会。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "speaker_name": "高渐飞",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "text": "你为什么要告诉我这些事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "speaker_name": "高渐飞",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "text": "为什么要救我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "speaker_name": "萧泪血",
      "listener": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "text": "因为我没有杀你，所以也不想让你死在别人手里。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "speaker_name": "高渐飞",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "text": "你当然也不想让我这柄剑落在别人手里。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "speaker_name": "萧泪血",
      "listener": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "speaker_name": "高渐飞",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "text": "你既然已经有了一件天下无双的武器，难道还想要这柄剑？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "speaker_name": "萧泪血",
      "listener": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "text": "我不想要。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "speaker_name": "萧泪血",
      "listener": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "text": "如果我想要，它早已是我的了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "speaker_name": "高渐飞",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "text": "那么你为什么要关心它？难道这柄剑和你这个人之间也有某种特别的关系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "speaker_name": "高渐飞",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "text": "你的箱子和我的剑，都是出自同一人之手，你和我之间是不是也会有某种特别的关系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_jian_fei",
      "speaker_name": "高渐飞",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei_xue",
      "text": "这些事你为什么不肯告诉我？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    }
